"title": "5943: self-deception",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5943: self-deception",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The state of individuals or nations who do not face up to their sin, their spiritual state or their future with any realism. It also describes those who presume upon their relationship with God or their own ability, or who have a misplaced trust in idols.</p>\n<h2>Those who are deceived over their sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1JN 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:1-Ps36:4\">PSA 36:1–36:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:34-Jer2:35\">JER 2:34–2:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9-Jer17:10\">JER 17:9–17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:10\">1JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Those who are deceived over their spiritual state</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:13-Matt23:15\">MAT 23:13–23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23-Matt23:33\">MAT 23:23–23:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42-Luke11:52\">LUK 11:42–11:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:33-John8:34\">JHN 8:33–8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:39-John8:47\">JHN 8:39–8:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22-Jas1:26\">JAS 1:22–1:26</a></p>\n<h2>Those who are deceived concerning the future</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:16\">JAS 4:13–4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:31\">JER 5:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13-Jer6:14\">JER 6:13–6:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:10-Jer8:11\">JER 8:10–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:14-Jer14:16\">JER 14:14–14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:16-Jer23:18\">JER 23:16–23:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:7-Ezek13:9\">EZK 13:7–13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:5\">MIC 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:20\">LUK 12:16–12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Those who presume on their relationship with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:9-Jer7:11\">JER 7:9–7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:14-Deut29:21\">DEU 29:14–29:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:9-Jer37:10\">JER 37:9–37:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:8-Matt3:9\">MAT 3:8–3:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:8\">LUK 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:25-Luke13:27\">LUK 13:25–13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:41–25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:39-John8:47\">JHN 8:39–8:47</a></p>\n<h3>The value of circumcision</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:29\">ROM 2:17–2:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:19\">1CO 7:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:2-Phil3:7\">PHP 3:2–3:7</a></p>\n<h2>Those who presume on their own ability</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18-1Cor3:20\">1CO 3:18–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3-Obad1:4\">OBA 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33-Matt26:35\">MAT 26:33–26:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27-Mark14:31\">MRK 14:27–14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:33-Luke22:34\">LUK 22:33–22:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:37-John13:38\">JHN 13:37–13:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:12\">2CO 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:3\">GAL 6:3</a></p>\n<h2>Those who deceive themselves about the acceptability of their worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:11–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:2-Isa58:7\">ISA 58:2–58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:2-Jer7:8\">JER 7:2–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:21-Jer7:29\">JER 7:21–7:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6-Mal1:14\">MAL 1:6–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:7\">MAT 6:7</a></p>\n<h2>Those who have a misplaced trust in their own righteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:12\">PRO 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2-Isa65:5\">ISA 65:2–65:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></p>\n<h2>Those who have a misplaced trust in idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:20–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:17-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:17–44:20</a></p>",
